# ðŸ“¦ `.gitattributes` for `search_explainer`

```gitattributes
# Ensure consistent line endings (force LF on all text files)
* text=auto eol=lf

# Python files
*.py text eol=lf

# Markdown docs
*.md text eol=lf

# Jupyter Notebooks
*.ipynb text

# DuckDB database file: mark as binary (avoids accidental text diffs)
*.duckdb binary

# VS Code settings
.vscode/* text

# JSON files
*.json text eol=lf

# Explicitly set linguist-detectable languages (optional, improves GitHub language stats)
*.py linguist-language=Python
*.md linguist-language=Markdown

# Shell scripts
*.sh text eol=lf
```

âœ… **Purpose:**
- Normalize line endings across platforms
- Treat binary files properly
- Improve language detection on GitHub
- Provide predictable diffs and behavior

